{"tid":352776,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"00388港交所業績報告","createTime":"2017-08-09T04:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T07:51:29.000Z","uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2be6af16f0a39202eb859fa04fb37e6c35ce1b","tid":352776,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"截至 2017 年 6 月 30 日止六個月（2017 年上半年）的收入及其他收益較 2016 年同期（2016 年上半年）高出 10%。<br />\n期內的主要摘要包括：<br />\n1.上市公司數目增加，新上市衍生權證以及牛熊證數目亦有所增長，使聯交所上市費收入上升；<br />\n2.公司資金及保證金的投資收益淨額大幅上升；<br />\n從雷曼清盤人收回一次性清盤後利息 5,500 萬元；及<br />\n<br />\n3.交易及結算費略減，因為包括商品的衍生產品成交量減少已抵銷了現貨市場成交額的穩健增幅。<br />\n<br />\n4.整體營運支出較 2016 年上半年增加 1%。扣除索回與美國倉庫訴訟有關的法律費用的一次性保險賠款 2,300 萬元，營運支出較上一年同期增加 3%。<br />\n<br />\n5.2017 年上半年的 EBITDA 利潤率為 72%，較 2016 年上半年增加 2%，反映收入增加及審慎管理成本。<br />\n股東應佔溢利增加 17%至 34.93 億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nreport：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2017/0809/LTN20170809182_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2017%2F0809%2FLTN20170809182_C.pdf&d=K7m9CDySsgaXUDngZw0451KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=9bc732c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2017/0809/LTN20170809182_C.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"2a7dfd6fd0ed8a0349f685a9c07e11c72a600ff8","tid":352776,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bb23fbb86ca521b4ceb185957a40c02ca6e9bf","tid":352776,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe2874e615423b1a792cd7a65430094bc99632d","tid":352776,"uid":72825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T